introduction: 马克斯是厌倦了盗窃和辣妹。决定改变生活方向，这家伙开始当司机发现恐怖，他的老板是没有其他比五宝贝不同年龄，所有的邪恶，特别是仆人。一个罕见的外观诱人的珍妮的感觉。一个巨大的冲击来自法国的电影时代的黄金时代，这巴黎电影院上映的电影。Max is tired of burglaries and babes. Determined to change direction in life, this guy begins working as a chauffeur and discovers in horror that his boss is none other than five babes of various ages, all vicious, particularly the servant. One of the uncommon appearances by the tantalizing Jenny Feeling. A giant hit from the golden age of France's Cinema X era, this film debuted in Paris cinemas.
